/// A lint-dirty class: the trailing `^` on the last expression is redundant
/// (Beamtalk returns the last expression implicitly). `beamtalk lint` must flag
/// it and exit non-zero. The source is otherwise fmt-clean.
Object subclass: CliLintDetects

  /// Return a greeting string (with a redundant explicit return).
  class greet => ^"hi"
